br />\n真係會爆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e6003fc0565cc666ef7b84a26da3a7a0f5c582","tid":1735503,"uid":51724,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好學日本人用40L汽油由底層開始燒漫畫工作室"},{"pid":"ddb976024bff94441a673fa3357a31f0e695e588","tid":1735503,"uid":55378,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"本身住狗宿既話輕鬆啦<br />\n深夜時分計好看更巡樓時間<br />\n帶大量電油，幾袋助燃物去低層<br />\n係逃生出口附近位置倒定電油同擺助燃物<br />\n係幾個底層單位門口倒油入屋，點火<br />\n走人順便鎖逃生門，係出口附近再點火<br />\n確保可以燒熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非狗宿住戶就最好組隊<br />\n先偷偷潛入，控制看更唔比佢報警<br />\n然後係出口倒定油放助燃物，有人想逃出即刻點火<br />\n睇下爬唔爬到去底層住戶窗口<br />\n搵硬物掟爆佢之後掟幾個火魔<br />\n要最好圍住棟樓搵4個單位以上<br />\n想食燒狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c2c1fa1ea29ba16b263f4cc0632177bb492efa","tid":1735503,"uid":55378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa230b65a9d866405e336c51083434b77bdf5655","tid":1735503,"uid":112205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1xd2r4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1xd2r4.jpg&h=3bd4ef8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救細佬仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"浪費左勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日光日白行動...<br />\n大家有決心既同時都要有計劃<br />\n盡量做到全身而退"},{"pid":"8b11f90d07c162790d7fe9a9d6b34bd35d6ac322","tid":1735503,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97c2c1fa1ea29ba16b263f4cc0632177bb492efa","tid":1735503,"uid":55378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa230b65a9d866405e336c51083434b77bdf5655","tid":1735503,"uid":112205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1xd2r4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=